[[Gumbapamwe]] (System) rinoreva kubatanidzwa pamwe munzvimbo imwe kwezvinhu zvine ukama huri kutarirwa.  Gumbapamwe rine zvinhu zvinobatirana, nekurarama, nekudyidzana pamwe munzvimbo yakatarwa. 

Kuti titsanangure Gumbapamwe tinogona kusanganisira: nhengo dzirimo;  zvinotaura mashandirwo emabasa;  mitemo inotonga nhengo dzirimo; uye zvinyorwa zvinotaura ukama huripo pakati penhengo (elements, stakeholders) idzi; nekutara miganhu yerumana rweGumbapamwe, uye miganhu yezvinotenderwa kana kusatenderwa kuitika kana kuti kuva nhengo.  Gumbapamwe rine ukama hunosimbiswa ne[[tsazaniso]] pakati pezvinopimwa (equations & relationships), maitirwo ezvirongwa (procedures & protocols), zvinyanye (extrema), zvichingodaro. 

Gumbapamwe - ''co-existing or working combined together''.
